The paper focuses on build automation tools and package managers, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The study analyzes the presence of bloated dependencies, which is a software development issue (cs.SD). The paper also proposes a tool to analyze Maven artifacts, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
